Output final answer with the format <<<answer>>>

def base6_to_base10(n):
    """Convert a base-6 number to base-10."""
    return int(str(n), 6)

def base10_to_base8(n):
    """Convert a base-10 number to base-8."""
    return oct(n)[2:]

# Convert base-6 number 200 to base-10
base_10_number = base6_to_base10(200)

# Convert the base-10 number to base-8
base_8_number = base10_to_base8(base_10_number)
